import React from 'react'
import PageTemplate from 'src/components/PageTemlate'
import './style.css'
import Input from '../Input'

const SignIn = () => {
  return (
    <PageTemplate title='Sign In'>
      <form className='form'>
        <Input />
      </form>
    </PageTemplate>
  )
}

export default SignIn
